ERP105501.description: Large scale RNA-Seq analysis was performed to investigate the transcriptomic response to osteoarthritis in cartilage and investigate potential subgroups of patients. Data were collected from intact knee cartilage (posterior lateral condyle) from at total of 60 patients with osteoarthritis (OA) following total knee replacement and 10 control non-OA patients following amputation.
ERP105501.protocol_description: RNA-Seq analysis of human osteoarthritic intact cartilage following total knee replacement
ERP105501.title: RNA-Seq analysis of human osteoarthritic intact cartilage following total knee replacement
